o8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FNYo8y.png&h=1533e1b3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己男人老狗扮女人都仲要拎出黎show俾人睇，狗真係冇咩尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要既證據呀垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/105116_e2f1e1857b5171f719b054b06c7a6f56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F105116_e2f1e1857b5171f719b054b06c7a6f56.jpg&h=a8d74252&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=692315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beautyexchange.com.hk%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D692315&d=iCT20ADNahQx85AIReXcu8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3c8cd3ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.beautyexchange.com.hk/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=692315</a><br />\n成個LIHKG得你條傻鳩會假膠當起底<br />\n咁撚柒就咪上網啦</blockquote><br />\non9仔，講過好多次唔係真假膠既問題，係你本人柒，俾本癲狗玩，大家又睇得開心，果900幾個like就係最好證明啦，你唔好咁天真成日貼哩篇野去為自己掩飾啦，篇野只係證明到你有可能係抄人，但證明唔到你本人身高體重係假架囉，得d咁流既所謂證據就慳d啦垃圾，再講，都話個重點唔係你係真定假，而係你柒，各位睇我撚你撚得好開心呀，知唔知呀閱讀障礙?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n柒咗就柒咗啦，你貼出嚟啲所謂證據都係本宮喺beautyexchange抄過嚟改篇嘅post嚟，咁撚柒仲話自己撚緊狗，自high當贏呀又？</blockquote><br />\n你條柒頭都識話改篇啦，咪改到個主角同自己一樣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />被人拆穿糗哂就死兜爛兜轉移視線，正垃圾，唔好避啦傻閪，有900幾人讚我篇撚鳩你既整合wo，點樣成個飲食版得我一個法呢? 點呀? 你睇唔睇到呀? 係唔係果900幾人都係虛構出黎架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />回應下啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?post=146504fce6a0cf892fe058c5961a580348e883bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?post=146504fce6a0cf892fe058c5961a580348e883bc</a><br />\n<br />\n係時候表演下你既呀Q精神啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你將假膠beauty exchange post貼出嚟有900正評就代表你真係起咗底？任何人喺LIHKG開post屌柒肥絲大隻都有正評㗎喎，你其他post全部負評就知你係垃圾靠用本宮嚟獲得正評啦，仲好意思講出嚟？你仲要借本宮上位借到幾時？唔係你開咁多肥絲post，呢度有撚人識你咩垃圾，你開post啲人都係入嚟等睇本宮貼你整合咋傻閪，啲人見到你就聯想到本宮，你永遠都活喺本宮陰影之下咋廢物</blockquote><br />\n叫你表現呀叫精神你就真係使出渾身解數黎試範，good boy (摸下你個狗頭先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n你做未回應我果900幾個正評支持我撚鳩你既post wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我其他post負評加埋都唔多我一個post900幾個正評既10份1啦，仲好意思講? d野唔係你唔提，你唔講，避開就代表冇架，再貼多次先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?post=146504fce6a0cf892fe058c5961a580348e883bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?post=146504fce6a0cf892fe058c5961a580348e883bc</a><br />\n<br />\n又要俾本癲撚，又要發火，廢到咁就唔好出黎吠引人恥笑啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續表演扮睇唔到啦，好玩好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d9a4e8772b7276c66fb81dbaef70e1c82f453a","tid":316240,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n自己男人老狗扮女人都仲要拎出黎show俾人睇，狗真係冇咩尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要既證據呀垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<stron